						{
							singleType="STRING";
							value="A Supply stockpile is located in the village of Tinobu, we suspect it is lightly guarded by a meagre force, however do not underestimate their capabilities. Intel suggests two trucks filled with fuel and supplies, if CSAT is delivering fuel, one can only guess what they'll equip the Syndikat with.<br/><br/>Do not set off the charges on the Stockpile too early! It will trigger the alarm which will cause the reaction force at the Monyet Airfield to move out. Ensure you are ready at the Ambush site prior to destroying the trucks.";
